<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Health Project</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../styles/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" />
</head>

<body>

    <div>



        <!-- <ul class="navbar">
            <li><a href="aboutus.html">Learn More</a></li>
            <li><a href="index.html">Vegipe</a></li>
        </ul> -->

        <div class="hero-image" src="../images/hero.jpg">
            <section class="hero-text">
                <h1>Vegipe</h1>
                <h2>Vegetarian and Vegan Recipes</h2>
            </section>

        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="about-us">
            <h2>Mission Statement</h2>
            <p class="mission"> Creating a platform for people to get vegetarian and vegan options
                for
                some of their favorite unhealthy guilty pleasures
            </p>

        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="api-section form-image">


            <div class="results">
                <form action="/search" method="GET">
                    <div class="form">
                        <label for="userInput"><span class="form-title">What kind of recipe do you want?</span></label>
                        <input name="userInput" type="text" class="ghost-input" placeholder="ex: tacos" required>
                        <br>
                        <label for="vOv"><span class="form-title">Vegan or Vegetarian?</span></label>
                        <input name="vOv" type="text" class="ghost-input" placeholder="" required>
                        <br>
                        <input class="submit" type="submit" class="ghost-button" value="Get Your Recipes!">
                    </div>
                </form>

                <div class="recipe-container">
                    <% if(title){ %>
                    <p><span class="api-title">Recipe Name: </span><%= title %></p>
                    <p><span class="api-title">Ready in: </span><%= readyTime %></p>
                    <p> <a href="<%= url %>" target="_blank" role="button">Check the recipe here!</a></p>
                    <% } %>
                </div>

                <div class="recipe-container">
                    <% if(title2){ %>
                    <p><span class="api-title">Recipe Name: </span><%= title2 %></p>
                    <p><span class="api-title">Ready in: </span><%= readyTime2 %></p>
                    <p> <a href="<%= url2 %>" target="_blank" role="button">Check the recipe here!</a></p>
                    <% } %>
                </div>

                <div class="recipe-container">
                    <% if(title3){ %>
                    <p><span class="api-title">Recipe Name: </span><%= title3 %></p>
                    <p><span class="api-title">Ready in: </span><%= readyTime3 %></p>
                    <p> <a href="<%= url3 %>" target="_blank" role="button">Check the recipe here!</a></p>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="recipe-container">
                <% if(error){ %>
                <p><%= error %></p>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-us section2">
            <h2>Learn More</h2>
            <p>Founded by a group of highly motivated individuals who sought out to increase awareness in their
                communities of healthy eating options and to show great alternatives to foods that otherwise would be
                harmful to our body.

                With impacts being felt most in black and brown communities healthy eating is a habit that needs to
                begin with us! By making recipe alternatives free and accessible to everyone we are hoping to boost the
                trend of healthy eating alternatives and change lives for generations to come!
                <br>
                <br>
                Unhealthy diet and lack of physical activity are leading global risks to health.
                A healthy diet includes Fruit, vegetables, legumes (e.g. lentils and beans), nuts and whole grains (e.g.
                unprocessed maize, millet, oats, wheat and brown rice).

                <br>We know that it can be hard to find healthy foods
                that
                taste great but <i>Vegipe</i> makes it possible
                and accessible to everyone!<br>
            </p>

        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">

        <div class="logo_div">
            <img class="logo" src="../images/logo.png" alt="our logo">
        </div>
        <p>&#169; Vegipe


            <a href="https://www.twitter.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i class="fa fa-instagram"></i>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i class="fa fa-facebook"> </i>
            </a>

        </p>



    </footer>

</body>

</html>